  m_Name: Update_v1_1_36
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  version: 1135
  sections:
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    h2Heading: 
    h3Heading: 
    bulletPoints: []
    text: '1.1.35 is a minor update with some bug fixes and tweaks

'
    links: []
    highlightObjects: []
    actions: []
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    h2Heading: 
    h3Heading: New Features
    bulletPoints:
    - 'Added a new weapon name HUD element which checks for a DisplayName behaviour
      and shows it on the HUD '
    text: 
    links: []
    highlightObjects: []
    actions: []
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    h2Heading: 
    h3Heading: Component Changes
    bulletPoints:
    - Added reload speed animation parameters to reloader modules
    - Added a "start includes reload" setting to incremental reloaders for start
      animations that include loading a shell
    - Added setting to HUD interaction progress bar to disable matching colour to
      crosshair
    - Exposed crosshair colour options for in-game menu in inspector
    - Added "Spring Return" settings to BetterSpringRecoilHandler to allow recoil
      which doesn't spring back to original location
    - Changed PhysicsBulletCasing to use ray casting before switching to rigidbody
      for better interpolation
    text: 
    links: []
    highlightObjects: []
    actions: []
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    h2Heading: 
    h3Heading: Script Changes
    bulletPoints:
    - Added "duplicateBehaviour" property to IInventory to fix a bug with auto-switching
      on replacing weapon
    - Added "DropItem(IQuickSlotItem item)" method to IQuickSlots to allow swapping
      items that share a quick slot
    text: The following changes could cause issues with custom scripts that reference
      the modified interfaces or classes
    links: []
    highlightObjects: []
    actions: []
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    h2Heading: 
    h3Heading: Extension Changes
    bulletPoints:
    - Updated the URP and HDRP extension packages for better coverage of materials
      and prefabs
    text: The following changes might need extension packages re-importing
    links: []
    highlightObjects: []
    actions: []
